dictionary.name: stable
dictionary.description: Rule is considered as stable and may be used in production systems or dashboards

dictionary.name: experimental
dictionary.description: Experimental rule that could lead to false positives results or be noisy

dictionary.name: test
dictionary.description: An almost stable rule that possibly could require some fine tuning

dictionary.name: deprecated
dictionary.description: Rule is replace or cover by another one

dictionary.name: unsupported
dictionary.description: Rule can not be use in its current state

dictionary.name: contains
dictionary.description: Modifier: puts * wildcards around the values, such that the value is matched anywhere in the field.

dictionary.name: all
dictionary.description: Modifier: Normally, lists of values were linked with OR in the generated query

dictionary.name: startswith
dictionary.description: Modifier: The value is expected at the beginning of the field's content

dictionary.name: endswith
dictionary.description: Modifier: The value is expected at the end of the field's content

dictionary.name: re
dictionary.description: Modifier: value is handled as regular expression by backends

dictionary.name: base64
dictionary.description: Modifier: The value is encoded with Base64

dictionary.name: base64offset
dictionary.description: Modifier: If a value might appear somewhere in a base64-encoded value the representation might change depending on the position in the overall value

dictionary.name: utf16le
dictionary.description: Modifier: transforms value to UTF16-LE encoding

dictionary.name: utf16be
dictionary.description: Modifier: transforms value to UTF16-BE encoding

dictionary.name: utf16
dictionary.description: Modifier: prepends a byte order mark and encodes UTF16

dictionary.name: windash
dictionary.description: Modifier: Add a new variant where all - occurrences are replaced with /

dictionary.name: informational
dictionary.description: Rule is intended for enrichment of events

dictionary.name: low
dictionary.description: Notable event but rarely an incident

dictionary.name: medium
dictionary.description: Relevant event that should be reviewed manually

dictionary.name: high
dictionary.description: Relevant event that should trigger an internal alert

dictionary.name: critical
dictionary.description: Highly relevant event that indicates an incident
